attachments.text:
Thanks for coming to Talkapalooza! We would love to gather your feedback to understand how we can improve the event. Your honesty is greatly appreciated! 

The purpose of Talkapalooza is to strengthen the BYU MBA student community through giving students a platform to share stories, passions, and ideas with one another. Students will be able to learn about each other outside of a classroom/professional setting, and in turn be able to better appreciate the diversity of the student body, expand their worldviews, and build lasting relationships. It will also provide opportunities for student speakers to practice giving powerful presentations.

For more information, visit this link.
